00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about metamorphic rocks than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:11,200
Metamorphic rocks are formed deep within the Earth, where intense heat and pressure work their magic.

3
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:15,200
Imagine granite turning into gneiss, or limestone morphing into marble.

4
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,800
It's nature's own art!

5
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:22,800
Each metamorphic rock tells a story of its journey, shaped by temperature, pressure, and time.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:28,800
So, next time you see a rock, remember—it might just be hiding a remarkable transformation.

7
